        "description": {
          "value": "<p><strong>Fail-state boss.</strong> He exists only if the Rise of the Dragon runs its 10 rounds. A CR-25 cataclysm (~L24): the published guidance expects flight or heroic death, not victory — alternatively run @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.pathfinder-bestiary.Actor.uPxh3VpA80zZdWfx]{Blue Dragon (Ancient)} with double Elite-grade scaling. The fangs in the Crown remain indestructible whatever happens.</p>"
